### LangGraph Server 模拟 - 运行 Agent（带用户认证）
POST http://localhost:2024/runs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer demo-token-123

{
  "input": {
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "你好"}]
  },
  "context": {
    "user_name": "1"
  }
}

### LangGraph Server 模拟 - 运行 Agent（管理员认证）
POST http://localhost:2024/runs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer admin-token-456

{ 
  "input": {
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "你好"}]
  },
  "context": {
    "user_name": "2"
  }
}

### LangGraph Server 模拟 - 运行 Agent（无用户认证，应返回 401）
POST http://localhost:2024/runs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": {
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "你好"}]
  },
  "context": {
    "user_name": "2"
  }
}
